These scripts form a template/skeleton for the 
pipeline with which we are using Cortex on the 1000 Genomes project
Phase 2. The scripts are simple and not very polished, they 
are meant for you to use in your own compute infratructure,
parallelising as much as you can. See the PDF :
http://cortexassembler.sourceforge.net/cortex_phase2_recipe.pdf
for details
